### Test Application API

### 1. Login as Candidate
POST http://localhost:5001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "candidate@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

### 2. Login as Employer
POST http://localhost:5001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "employer@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

### 3. Create Application (Candidate only)
# Thay YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN bằng token từ login candidate
POST http://localhost:5001/applications
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "JOB_UUID_HERE",
  "cvId": "CV_UUID_HERE",
  "cvType": "uploaded",
  "coverLetter": "Tôi rất quan tâm đến vị trí này và tin rằng tôi phù hợp với yêu cầu công việc."
}

### 4. Get Application Details
GET http://localhost:5001/applications/APPLICATION_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN

### 5. Update Application (Candidate only - chỉ khi status = submitted)
PUT http://localhost:5001/applications/APPLICATION_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cvId": "NEW_CV_UUID_HERE",
  "cvType": "template",
  "coverLetter": "Updated cover letter"
}

### 6. Withdraw Application (Candidate only - chỉ khi status = submitted)
POST http://localhost:5001/applications/APPLICATION_UUID_HERE/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN

### 7. List My Applications (Candidate)
GET http://localhost:5001/applications/my-applications?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN

### 8. List My Applications with filters
GET http://localhost:5001/applications/my-applications?status=submitted&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN

### 9. List Job Applications (Employer only)
# Thay YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN bằng token từ login employer
GET http://localhost:5001/applications/jobs/JOB_UUID_HERE/applications?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN

### 10. List Job Applications with filters
GET http://localhost:5001/applications/jobs/JOB_UUID_HERE/applications?status=submitted&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN

### 11. Update Application Status (Employer only)
PUT http://localhost:5001/applications/APPLICATION_UUID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "reviewing"
}

### 12. Update Application Status to Interview
PUT http://localhost:5001/applications/APPLICATION_UUID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "interview"
}

### 13. Update Application Status to Accepted
PUT http://localhost:5001/applications/APPLICATION_UUID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "accepted"
}

### 14. Update Application Status to Rejected
PUT http://localhost:5001/applications/APPLICATION_UUID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "rejected"
}

### Test Error Cases

### 15. Try to create duplicate application (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5001/applications
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "SAME_JOB_UUID",
  "cvId": "SAME_CV_UUID",
  "cvType": "uploaded",
  "coverLetter": "Duplicate application"
}

### 16. Try to update withdrawn application (should fail)
PUT http://localhost:5001/applications/WITHDRAWN_APPLICATION_UUID/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_EMPLOYER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "reviewing"
}

### 17. Try to apply to expired job (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5001/applications
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CANDIDATE_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "EXPIRED_JOB_UUID",
  "cvId": "CV_UUID_HERE",
  "cvType": "uploaded"
}
